3-key macro pad
Slider #

*1. Ideate basic functions
2. Create basic paper sketch draft of design
3. Create prototype model in CAD
4. Figure out electronics (F-mouse board combined with breaker board)
5. System integration of main pcb, your designed breaker board, and the body.*

